metadata.name: TURF by Bobby Hundreds
metadata.description:
An artwork by Bobby Hundreds for 'Fund The Jump'.

JumpStart Designers is a 501(c)(3) non-profit created to provide computers & digital art programs to kids in underserved communities. With this fundraiser we will be able to provide 30 kids with the tools, education, and mentorship they need to succeed in the digital art world. This event was completely powered by MoonPay!
